{"case_id":"cc-L1-001-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"在 Cocos Creator 里，Node 和 Component 分别是什么？它们之间是什么关系？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_node_component"],"answer":"Node 更像场景里的一个对象/容器（有层级、位置、子节点等），Component 是挂在 Node 上的功能模块（脚本、渲染、碰撞等）。一个 Node 可以挂多个组件，组件通过 node 引用拿到挂载节点并操作它。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.6,"min_rubric_score":0.6,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L1-001-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"在 Cocos Creator 里，Node 和 Component 分别是什么？它们之间是什么关系？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_node_component"],"answer":"Node 是节点，Component 是组件，组件挂在节点上用来做功能。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.6,"min_coverage":0.4,"min_rubric_score":0.4,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L1-001-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"在 Cocos Creator 里，Node 和 Component 分别是什么？它们之间是什么关系？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_node_component"],"answer":"Component 是节点，Node 是组件，两个是一样的东西。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L1-002-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"简要解释一个组件的生命周期（例如 onLoad/start/update/onEnable/onDisable/onDestroy）大概在什么时候触发，各自适合做什么。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle"],"answer":"onLoad 通常用于初始化引用/注册事件；onEnable 在组件启用时触发适合恢复监听；start 在首帧 update 前适合依赖其他组件初始化完成后的逻辑；update 每帧执行做持续更新；onDisable 取消监听/暂停；onDestroy 做最终清理释放。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.6,"min_rubric_score":0.6,"expected_decision":"promote","expected_level_change":1}}
{"case_id":"cc-L1-002-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"简要解释一个组件的生命周期（例如 onLoad/start/update/onEnable/onDisable/onDestroy）大概在什么时候触发，各自适合做什么。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle"],"answer":"onLoad 初始化，start 开始，update 每帧更新，destroy 删除时调用。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.6,"min_coverage":0.4,"min_rubric_score":0.4,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L1-002-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L1","question_type":"explain","question":"简要解释一个组件的生命周期（例如 onLoad/start/update/onEnable/onDisable/onDestroy）大概在什么时候触发，各自适合做什么。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle"],"answer":"update 只会在 onDestroy 之后执行，start 是销毁用的。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L2-001-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"derive","question":"如果你要在组件里让一个节点以固定速度移动（与帧率无关），你会怎么写 update 逻辑？请给出关键公式/伪代码并说明注意点。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_coordinate_camera"],"answer":"在 update(dt) 里用 dt 做位移：this.node.position = this.node.position.add(this.dir.multiplyScalar(this.speed * dt))。注意 dt 单位是秒；避免直接用“每帧加固定值”；必要时限制 dt 过大导致瞬移。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.6,"min_rubric_score":0.6,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L2-001-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"derive","question":"如果你要在组件里让一个节点以固定速度移动（与帧率无关），你会怎么写 update 逻辑？请给出关键公式/伪代码并说明注意点。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_coordinate_camera"],"answer":"update 里 pos.x += speed * dt。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.7,"min_coverage":0.4,"min_rubric_score":0.5,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L2-001-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"derive","question":"如果你要在组件里让一个节点以固定速度移动（与帧率无关），你会怎么写 update 逻辑？请给出关键公式/伪代码并说明注意点。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_coordinate_camera"],"answer":"每帧 x += speed，不用 dt，这样最稳定。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L2-002-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"explain","question":"你会把“事件注册/解绑”（例如 input/自定义事件）放在生命周期的哪个阶段？为什么？如果不解绑会发生什么问题？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_events_input"],"answer":"一般在 onEnable 注册、onDisable 解绑（或 onLoad 注册、onDestroy 清理），取决于是否需要随启用/禁用切换。若不解绑，可能造成重复回调、内存泄漏、访问已销毁对象导致异常。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.6,"min_rubric_score":0.6,"expected_decision":"promote","expected_level_change":1}}
{"case_id":"cc-L2-002-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"explain","question":"你会把“事件注册/解绑”（例如 input/自定义事件）放在生命周期的哪个阶段？为什么？如果不解绑会发生什么问题？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_events_input"],"answer":"onLoad 注册，destroy 解绑。不解绑会重复触发。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.7,"min_coverage":0.5,"min_rubric_score":0.5,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L2-002-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L2","question_type":"explain","question":"你会把“事件注册/解绑”（例如 input/自定义事件）放在生命周期的哪个阶段？为什么？如果不解绑会发生什么问题？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_lifecycle","sp_cc_events_input"],"answer":"事件不用解绑，引擎会自动处理，不会有任何问题。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.2,"min_coverage":0.2,"min_rubric_score":0.3,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L3-002-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"compare","question":"资源加载与释放该如何设计，才能避免卡顿和内存泄漏？请说明至少一个 tradeoff（例如：缓存 vs 内存）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_update_perf","sp_cc_bundles"],"answer":"避免卡顿要做按需加载/预加载与分帧；避免泄漏要有明确的持有关系和释放时机（引用计数/统一资源管理）。tradeoff：缓存可减少重复加载但占内存；过度释放会造成频繁 IO/反复创建导致卡顿。可以用 bundles 分组，进界面加载、出界面释放，配合延迟释放与复用策略。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.7,"min_rubric_score":0.7,"expected_decision":"promote","expected_level_change":1}}
{"case_id":"cc-L3-002-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"compare","question":"资源加载与释放该如何设计，才能避免卡顿和内存泄漏？请说明至少一个 tradeoff（例如：缓存 vs 内存）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_update_perf","sp_cc_bundles"],"answer":"需要缓存资源，离开界面时释放，不然会内存涨。缓存太多会占内存。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.6,"min_coverage":0.5,"min_rubric_score":0.5,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L3-002-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"compare","question":"资源加载与释放该如何设计，才能避免卡顿和内存泄漏？请说明至少一个 tradeoff（例如：缓存 vs 内存）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_update_perf","sp_cc_bundles"],"answer":"内存上涨就重启游戏。加载越多越好，不需要释放。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L3-003-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"explain","question":"渲染性能里 draw calls / overdraw / batching 各意味着什么？在 Cocos 的 UI 场景里你会优先怎么排查与优化？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_render_perf","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"draw calls 多通常是 CPU 提交/状态切换开销；overdraw 多是像素重复绘制（UI/透明层叠很常见）；batching 用来减少 draw calls。UI 优先看透明/遮罩/层级导致的 overdraw，再看合批是否被材质/纹理打断；用 profiler/渲染统计验证瓶颈并对比优化前后。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.7,"min_rubric_score":0.7,"expected_decision":"promote","expected_level_change":1}}
{"case_id":"cc-L3-003-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"explain","question":"渲染性能里 draw calls / overdraw / batching 各意味着什么？在 Cocos 的 UI 场景里你会优先怎么排查与优化？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_render_perf","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"draw call 是渲染次数，batching 可以减少它。UI 卡就把图片压缩一下。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.5,"min_coverage":0.4,"min_rubric_score":0.4,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L3-003-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L3","question_type":"explain","question":"渲染性能里 draw calls / overdraw / batching 各意味着什么？在 Cocos 的 UI 场景里你会优先怎么排查与优化？","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_render_perf","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"draw call 越多越清晰，overdraw 是优化手段，batching 会让画质变差所以不要用。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L4-001-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"debug","question":"现象：进入/退出某个界面多次后越来越卡，内存也持续上涨。请给出一个可执行的排查路径（复现、观测点、可能原因、验证修复）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_debug_strategy","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"先稳定复现：连续开关界面 N 次，记录内存曲线与帧率。观测：1) profiler 看内存分类/对象数，2) 统计节点/组件数量是否累积，3) 记录资源加载与释放（是否有未释放的纹理/atlas/动画）。假设：事件未解绑、定时器/回调持有引用、资源缓存不释放、bundle 反复加载。验证：逐个关闭界面子模块、加日志确认释放函数是否调用、做最小场景复现。修复后再跑同样步骤确认曲线回落。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.7,"min_rubric_score":0.7,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L4-001-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"debug","question":"现象：进入/退出某个界面多次后越来越卡，内存也持续上涨。请给出一个可执行的排查路径（复现、观测点、可能原因、验证修复）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_debug_strategy","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"用 profiler 看一下内存哪里涨，可能是资源没释放。离开界面释放资源试试。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.6,"min_coverage":0.4,"min_rubric_score":0.5,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L4-001-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"debug","question":"现象：进入/退出某个界面多次后越来越卡，内存也持续上涨。请给出一个可执行的排查路径（复现、观测点、可能原因、验证修复）。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_debug_strategy","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_profiling"],"answer":"这是引擎问题，没办法排查，重启就好了。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}

{"case_id":"cc-L4-003-good","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"derive","question":"假设你要做“分包/按需加载”，请说明你会如何组织 bundles 与加载策略，并说明一个可能的风险与缓解方式。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_bundles","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_build_release"],"answer":"按业务场景拆 bundles（主包+常驻+各大功能界面/活动），公共依赖尽量下沉到 common bundle 避免重复。进入界面前预加载关键资源，首次进入用占位/分帧加载降低卡顿，退出界面延迟释放避免抖动。风险：依赖重复导致包体膨胀或运行时加载链很长；缓解：做依赖分析、统一依赖归属、为关键链路做预加载和缓存策略，并用发布前的包体/加载耗时回归验证。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.8,"min_coverage":0.7,"min_rubric_score":0.7,"expected_decision":"promote","expected_level_change":1}}
{"case_id":"cc-L4-003-mid","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"derive","question":"假设你要做“分包/按需加载”，请说明你会如何组织 bundles 与加载策略，并说明一个可能的风险与缓解方式。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_bundles","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_build_release"],"answer":"把资源分成几个 bundle，需要的时候加载，不用就释放。风险是加载慢，可以提前加载。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.6,"min_coverage":0.5,"min_rubric_score":0.5,"expected_decision":"hold","expected_level_change":0}}
{"case_id":"cc-L4-003-bad","topic_id":"cocos_dev_core","level":"L4","question_type":"derive","question":"假设你要做“分包/按需加载”，请说明你会如何组织 bundles 与加载策略，并说明一个可能的风险与缓解方式。","taxonomy_version":"tax_v0.1","taxonomy_id":"tax_cocos_dev_core","expected_subpoints":["sp_cc_bundles","sp_cc_assets_resources","sp_cc_build_release"],"answer":"分包就是把所有资源都拆开，越碎越好，风险没有。","expected":{"min_correctness":0.0,"min_coverage":0.0,"min_rubric_score":0.2,"expected_decision":"demote","expected_level_change":-1}}
